Package com.ilm.projecto_ilm_backend.dto.messages

Class MessagesPageDto

java.lang.Object
com.ilm.projecto_ilm_backend.dto.messages.MessagesPageDto
public class MessagesPageDto extends Object
Data Transfer Object for the messages page. This class encapsulates the data required to display messages related to a specific project, including the messages themselves, project name, project state, project members, and the type of user viewing the project.
